(32147, 'Sildenamax 100mg 8 tabs', 'سيلديناماكس 100مجم 8 قرص', '60', '86', 'Sildenafil', 'Egpi > heropharm', 'Tab', 'أقراص', '', 'Tonic for men', '100mg', 'Sildenafil is a phosphodiesterase-5 (PDE5) inhibitor that is predominantly employed for two primary indications:
